fields.name: 36 Gallon Planted Invert Tank
fields.flora: Cryptocoryne balansae, C. wendtii green, C. costata, C. lucens, Madagascar Lace, Anubias nana
fields.noteworthy_comments: The tylos are growing and reproducing amazingly in this environment. So are the shrimp. The planted tank is the way to go. If anybody wants plants for their tank I'll be doing a trim soon and would hate to throw it all away

fields.name: 8 Gallon Natural Walstad
fields.flora: Cryptocoryne lutea, C. lucens, Anubias nana, Ludwigia
fields.noteworthy_comments: This is a naturally planted spherical aquarium done in the Walstad Method. No Co2, no ferts, but a substrate of organic potting soil capped with sand. The plants have done great in this as have the shrimp and snails.
